14:31.510 --> 14:32.170
Jiang.

14:33.820 --> 14:34.760
Kalian berdua kenapa...

14:39.620 --> 14:40.340
Aku pergi dulu.

14:40.690 --> 14:42.110
Sampai jumpa, Senior Wen.

14:46.270 --> 14:47.510
Aku sepertinya mencium

14:47.530 --> 14:48.740
